REPORT.TITLE: Test Report
REPORT.SUBTITLE: GAP

TEST_SETUP.NAME: Description of Test Set-up
TEST_SETUP.TEXT: The Test System PTS for Bluetooth is running on a PC System.
The test system communicates with the Bluetooth Hardware via an HCI connection.
The tests are performed as remote tests and all communication between the Test System and the IUT is done via the radio interface.
